  "remarks": "LLC Navitron is a Russian company operating in the Russian high-tech sector. It develops and tests satellite navigation chips for use in the military industry. LLC Navitron cooperates with Russian companies operating in the military-industrial sector. It thus contributes to the military and technological strengthening of Russia and the development of its defence and security sectors. Therefore, LLC Navitron is supporting Russia’s military and industrial complex.",
